{
  "info": {
    "name": "Budojo API",
    "description": "Budojo REST API — v1. Import this collection into Postman and set the `base_url` variable (default: http://localhost:8000).\n\nAfter a successful login or register the `token` collection variable is stored automatically via the test script.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Returns `{\"status\":\"ok\"}` when the API is up and running."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\"status\":\"ok\"}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Mario Rossi\",\n  \"email\": \"mario@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password1!\",\n  \"password_confirmation\": \"Password1!\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": { "language": "json" }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Creates a new user account and returns the user data plus a Sanctum Bearer token.\n\n**Validation rules**\n- `name` — required, string, max 255\n- `email` — required, valid e-mail, unique\n- `password` — required, min 8, must include uppercase, lowercase, digit and symbol; confirmed via `password_confirmation`\n\n**Response `201 Created`**\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": { \"id\": 1, \"name\": \"Mario Rossi\", \"email\": \"mario@example.com\" },\n  \"token\": \"<sanctum-plain-text-token>\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "201 Created",
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Mario Rossi\",\n    \"email\": \"mario@example.com\"\n  },\n  \"token\": \"1|abc123xyz...\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Unprocessable Entity — email taken",
              "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
              "code": 422,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"The email has already been taken.\",\n  \"errors\": {\n    \"email\": [\"The email has already been taken.\"]\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Unprocessable Entity — missing fields",
              "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
              "code": 422,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"The name field is required. (and 2 more errors)\",\n  \"errors\": {\n    \"name\": [\"The name field is required.\"],\n    \"email\": [\"The email field is required.\"],\n    \"password\": [\"The password field is required.\"]\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"mario@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password1!\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": { "language": "json" }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Authenticates an existing user and returns a new Sanctum Bearer token.\n\n**Validation rules**\n- `email` — required, valid e-mail\n- `password` — required, string\n\n**Response `200 OK`**\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": { \"id\": 1, \"name\": \"Mario Rossi\", \"email\": \"mario@example.com\" },\n  \"token\": \"<sanctum-plain-text-token>\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Mario Rossi\",\n    \"email\": \"mario@example.com\"\n  },\n  \"token\": \"2|def456uvw...\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "401 Unauthorized — wrong credentials",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Invalid credentials.\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Unprocessable Entity — missing fields",
              "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
              "code": 422,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"The email field is required. (and 1 more error)\",\n  \"errors\": {\n    \"email\": [\"The email field is required.\"],\n    \"password\": [\"The password field is required.\"]\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
